# Electron preload and main

- Expose renderer-facing capabilities only through `contextBridge` in `electron-preload.ts` as properties of `window.faContentBridgeAPIs`.
- Implement API objects in `src-electron/contentBridgeAPIs/` and extend `src/globals.d.ts` plus `types/I_*.ts` when adding or changing shapes.
- Do not widen renderer `nodeIntegration` or expose raw `require`/`ipcRenderer` wholesale to fix shortcuts.
- Prefer narrow, typed methods; add Vitest tests under `contentBridgeAPIs/tests/` when behavior is non-trivial.
